These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, lemon, lime, pepper
1. the person eating watermelon is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3
3. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | watermelon | lemon | lime | pepper |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, lemonade, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | soy-milk | hot-chocolate | lemonade |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, traveling, sudoku, singing
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | sudoku | traveling | singing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, horror, western
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure | western | horror |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, badminton, snowboarding, cycling
