2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | cycling | snowboarding | badminton | skateboarding |

