.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, pineapple, onion, peach
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating pineapple is between the person eating eggplant and the person eating peach##2
3. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
4. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | peach | pineapple | eggplant | onion |

