.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, dubstep, electronic, d&b
1. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
4. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep | house | d&b |

 